    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Type of lace reuniting elements and motifs from bobbin and needle lace to form a harmonious piece. It can also contain mechanical elements such as tape and tulle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
